==Korean==

===Etymology===

From [[흰]] (''huin'', adjective form of [[희다]], "to be white") + [[넓적다리]] (''neolpjeokdari'', "thigh") + [[붉은]] (''bulgeun'', adjective form of [[붉다]], "to be red") + [[쥐]] (''jwi'', "white")

